Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97285,99871}You can't beat a hot bun\Nin winter, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100330,102081}Mmm. It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105335,108421}Oh, my. Meimi, that big mouth.\NIt's really un-ladylike!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111090,112800}Well then, I'll just have another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113301,114260}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115553,116679}It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125980,128399}Those are my buns!\NGive them back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130318,132445}Meimi, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134030,135323}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139035,141037}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146334,148336}Meimi, pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151339,153508}I'm so glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155218,157637}What's with that dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160014,163309}Run After a Jewel Thief!\NLittle, The Naughty Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166396,167355}Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168773,171526}He's quite popular\Nat that park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171818,174737}They say he goes off\Nwith whatever he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175071,177532}With a name like "Little"\Nand a big body like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177615,179117}what a strange thing to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179200,182245}But I feel sorry for Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:03.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182912,183996}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185081,188626}Little's original owner was\Ntransferred to work abroad…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188668,190253}because of his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192171,194674}Little was left with a friend…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195174,197593}but the friend's wife\Ndidn't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197719,200430}He doesn't get\Nany attention at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203307,204100}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205059,208688}He's trying to get attention\Nby taking people's things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:45.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222994,225329}This bun is really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230918,232712}Wasn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234589,235339}Here…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239886,240720}Go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251355,253483}Little! Here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254066,255151}Fetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266454,268039}Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272293,273669}Haneoka, what do you\Nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273711,275797}Have you got some kind of\Ngrudge against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276172,277215}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277256,279550}It's your fault for reading\Nthe paper while walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:43.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280092,283721}I read the paper to gather\Ninformation on St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283763,285139}Not very much help, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285181,286724}She just keeps slipping\Npast you every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286808,288184}What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288226,289268}What about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291437,294857}The Jewel Thief Appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300446,302198}Hey, you! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306077,307995}Hey, I said hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310748,313209}Darn dog running\Ninto a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318130,319257}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319423,321968}He hides the things\Nhe steals in that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322009,323010}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326472,328599}You shouldn't do\Nthings like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330726,331644}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333563,335398}You two…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340778,341821}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341904,344824}Hey, brother, that's it!\NThe raccoon stuffed-animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345491,347326}I'll go get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348035,350663}What are you doing?!\NGet to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350705,352373}Ouch! What are you doing, brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352456,353666}Hey, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354333,356127}I'd like this stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356294,358045}Yes, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358087,360506}"Stuffed Toy Shop CHILD"\NHere you are.\NThanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368180,370266}Little is an innocent, good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370892,372768}Not the best looking, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373185,376105}Is it possible you're\Njealous of Little and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377398,379859}Don't be stupid.\NI like you best of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391746,393706}Akira, everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393915,396918}Your prayers will surely\Nreach God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:47.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401756,407219}That boy, Akira, took the\Nstuffed animal raccoon from Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408387,409889}He likes her so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409972,411933}he probably did it\Nto get her attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415978,418356}Akira, regretting what\Nhe had done…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418356,421025}tried to return the\Nstuffed-animal right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424612,427281}But someone stole the\Nstuffed animal from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427657,429909}Who would do such\Na terrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430159,431577}Well, the culprit is a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431619,432411}A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433037,435081}Do you mean, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:21.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436540,441504}We know that the stuffed animal\Nis somewhere in that park but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442254,443297}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448344,450012}I'll get that stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452098,453140}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454433,455685}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457311,459313}Maybe he's not here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460648,461649}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461691,463234}He's not over here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463859,464902}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468280,470658}The stuffed animal is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473536,474912}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478749,480835}Hey! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481544,482461}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482503,484630}Why did you bring the dog along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485423,486841}What could I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486882,489218}He wouldn't let go\Nof the stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490594,491846}Let's just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506610,508237}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508320,510322}Shut up! I just got\Nthe baby to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511365,512950}Oh, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512992,514577}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515536,516787}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516954,518330}Little, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535639,537224}Hey, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550279,552198}You caused a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554700,556535}He's the one that\Nmade the mistake…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556577,558370}and put the toy out for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558871,561749}Hey brother, let's stop doing\Nthis stuffed-animal business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562041,564668}We're supposed to be jewel thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565044,566504}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566587,569882}The stuffed animal-toy shop is\Nto camouflage the jewel thefts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570216,572218}How dumb can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572259,573219}Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573260,575304}What counts is that\Nthe jewel is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577932,580434}We hide the stolen jewels\Nin the stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580476,581602}When things cool down…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581644,583646}we can take them to another\Ncity and pawn 'em off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583854,585481}It's a great racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585606,588067}The only thing left\Nis to get rid of the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593531,595074}You're gonna kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595199,596200}That's outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596450,598494}Even if he's a dog…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598536,600454}we can't let anybody\Nwho knows about us get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608838,610464}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612174,613968}Where has he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616095,617930}Hold him still!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617972,620516}Brother, I don't like\Nthis sort of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626272,627815}You imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628149,629400}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630234,631277}After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632653,633779}Little…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636031,637116}Little!
Comment: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:38.65,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:638659,638659}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:44.66,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:644665,644665}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:49.62,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:649628,649628}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652131,653549}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653591,655134}You're alright, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656969,658596}Hey, that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662016,663100}Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665811,667771}Where have you been all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670441,671567}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674403,675779}Yipes! Get out of sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676697,678282}What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682119,684079}What? Is there something wrong here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686040,688417}Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696759,698719}That's Yoko's raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698761,700346}Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703057,704516}Little, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705142,708437}Ah, may I take a look around\Nin this warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708938,711190}This place is off-limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711482,712399}Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712441,713275}What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713651,714610}Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714610,716153}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721075,723285}Can we just let\Nthem go like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:04.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724119,724954}We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724995,726247}We'll have to change plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736090,737174}Mr. Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738884,740594}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:31.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747685,751272}"I'll be picking up a\Nstuffed-toy raccoon…"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751689,752856}"from the number one warehouse.\N– St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753691,755526}A stuffed-toy raccoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756986,759405}What's she gonna do\Nwith a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765244,768706}Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774044,775045}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777464,778799}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780759,782845}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796317,800029}Looks like it's necessary for St. Tail\Nto make an appearance after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:24.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800404,804074}But I wonder what the raccoon\Nis doing in a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:28.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804867,808704}That storage area is rumored\Nto be connected with criminal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808746,810039}Be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810372,811248}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811373,812374}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812416,814543}I'm only going there\Nto get that stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816712,820174}May the blessings\Nof God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842571,845908}Not even St. Tail would be able\Nto get past this security.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:10.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846200,850079}Well, there's no way into the\Nwarehouse other than this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850287,852081}Don't underestimate St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852456,853999}Stay on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854291,855209}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856210,857419}Asuka Jr! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858712,859838}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865135,866470}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866845,868639}Everyone! Stay at your posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868722,869556}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875312,877815}I've got you now, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883654,885614}A rubber doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885989,887324}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889201,890577}Asuka Jr!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896750,897835}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898293,899420}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899461,900587}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907469,908595}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908679,910848}St. Tail has gotten\Ninto the warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924903,927948}St. Tail, today I'll get\Nyou for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934455,935414}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938292,940002}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943255,944756}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949887,951263}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959313,960272}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960606,962274}Yoko's raccoon isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965777,966945}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967279,968113}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970908,972701}Hold it! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975204,978165}Where could Yoko's\Nraccoon have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994806,995682}Little?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996517,998018}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998977,1000229}Wait, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006151,1008153}Could the raccoon be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013909,1015244}Someone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019498,1020415}Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021208,1022751}This is bad! Hide over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027673,1028924}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038100,1040227}Where are you?! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055325,1056660}You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062416,1063834}Thank you, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065836,1066878}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086690,1087858}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113175,1115302}You're jewel thieves, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117137,1118639}So what if we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120599,1121433}Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121475,1123477}hand that thing over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138325,1140285}Hurry up and hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145040,1146750}What! That mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192587,1194005}A diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204266,1205142}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:12.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209104,1212482}Akira returned the\Nraccoon to Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212524,1214609}They've really become close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215152,1217279}The jewel thieves\Nhave been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217320,1219281}So I guess we can consider\Nthis case closed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219448,1221450}We owe it all to Little, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221867,1223869}That's right.\NLittle deserves the credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233795,1236381}That dog, why was he\Nat the warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238842,1239843}Little…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240010,1241261}I'll race you to that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:42.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242304,1242971}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243388,1244222}Go!
